       "            n_jobs\n",
       "            <span class=\"param-doc-description\">n_jobs: int, default=None<br><br>Does not have any effect.<br><br>.. deprecated:: 1.8<br>   `n_jobs` is deprecated in version 1.8 and will be removed in 1.10.</span>\n",
